#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:143
msgid "Bank transactions"
msgstr "עסקאות בנק"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started/multi_currency.rst:145
msgid ""
"When creating or importing bank transactions, the amount is in the company's "
"main currency. To input a **foreign currency**, select a currency in "
"the :guilabel:`Foreign Currency`. Once selected, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Amount` in your main currency for it to automatically get "
"converted in the foreign currency in the :guilabel:`Amount in Currency "
