"journal <../bank>` used to receive SDD payments for the mandate."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`SDD Scheme` depends on the type of customer. "
"Select :guilabel:`CORE` for B2C customers and :guilabel:`B2B` for B2B "
"customers."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`סכימת SDD` תלויה בסוג הלקוח. בחר :guilabel:`CORE` עבור לקוחות B2C "
"ו:guilabel:`B2B` עבור לקוחות B2B."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:78
msgid ""
":guilabel:`End Date`: select a date after which the mandate is closed "
"automatically. If this is left empty, the mandate remains active until it "
"closed or revoked."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`תאריך סיום`: בחר תאריך שלאחריו ההרשאה נסגרת אוטומטית. אם זה נשאר "
"ריק, ההרשאה נשארת פעילה עד שהיא נסגרת או מבוטלת."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:82
msgid ""
"The B2B scheme is an optional scheme, offered exclusively to business "
"payers. Some banks or businesses might not accept B2B SDD."
msgstr ""
"סכימת B2B היא סכימה אופציונלית, המוצעת אך ורק למשלמים עסקיים. בנקים או עסקים "
"מסוימים עשויים שלא לקבל SDD מסוג B2B."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:85
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Print` to generate a PDF of the mandate form, then send it "
"to the customer for signature."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:87
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Validate` to activate the mandate."
msgstr "יש ללחוץ על :guilabel:`Validate` כדי להפעיל את ההרשאה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:90
msgid ""
"To print the mandate form after the mandate has been validated, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` (:guilabel:`gear`) icon, then select :guilabel:`Mandate "
"form`."
msgstr ""
"כדי להדפיס את טופס ההרשאה לאחר שההרשאה אומתה, יש ללחוץ על סמל :icon:`fa-cog` "
"(:guilabel:`gear`), ולאחר מכן לבחור :guilabel:`Mandate form`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:93
msgid ""
"Once an SDD mandate is active, subsequent SDD payments can be generated via "
"Odoo and :ref:`uploaded to your online banking interface <accounting/"
"sepa_payments/XML>`. Customers with an active SDD mandate can also use this "
"payment method for :doc:`online purchases <../../payment_providers/sdd>`."
msgstr ""
"לאחר שהרשאת SDD פעילה, ניתן ליצור תשלומי SDD נוספים דרך Odoo :ref:`ולהעלות "
"אותם לממשק הבנקאות המקוון שלך <accounting/sepa_payments/XML>`. לקוחות עם "
"הרשאת SDD פעילה יכולים גם להשתמש באמצעי תשלום זה עבור :doc:`רכישות מקוונות "
"<../../payment_providers/sdd>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:100
msgid "Closing or revoking a mandate"
msgstr "סגירה או ביטול של הרשאה"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:102
msgid ""
"To close or revoke a mandate, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Customers "
"--> Direct Debit Mandates`, select the relevant mandate, and "
"click :guilabel:`Close` or :guilabel:`Revoke`."
msgstr ""
"כדי לסגור או לבטל הרשאה, עבור אל :menuselection:`חשבונאות --> לקוחות --> "
"הרשאות חיוב ישיר`, בחר את ההרשאה הרלוונטית ולחץ על :guilabel:`סגור` "
"או :guilabel:`בטל`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:105
msgid ""
"**Closing** a mandate updates the mandate's end day to the current day. "
"Invoices issued after the present day will not be processed with an SDD "
"payment. **Revoking** a mandate immediately disables it. No SDD payment can "
"be registered anymore, regardless of the invoice's date. However, payments "
"that have already been registered are still included in the next :ref:`SDD "
"XML file <accounting/sepa_payments/XML>`."
msgstr ""
"**סגירת** הרשאה מעדכנת את יום הסיום של ההרשאה ליום הנוכחי. חשבוניות שהונפקו "
"לאחר היום הנוכחי לא יעובדו עם תשלום SDD. **ביטול** הרשאה משבית אותה מיד. לא "
"ניתן לרשום עוד תשלום SDD, ללא קשר לתאריך החשבונית. עם זאת, תשלומים שכבר "
"נרשמו עדיין כלולים ב:ref:`קובץ XML של SDD <accounting/sepa_payments/XML>` "
"הבא."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:112
msgid ""
"Mandates are automatically closed 36 months after the date of the last "
"collection."
msgstr "הרשאות נסגרות אוטומטית 36 חודשים לאחר תאריך הגבייה האחרונה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:113
msgid "Closed or revoked mandates cannot be reactivated."
msgstr "לא ניתן להפעיל מחדש הרשאות סגורות או מבוטלות."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:118
msgid "Processing SDD payments"
msgstr "עיבוד תשלומי SDD"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:120
msgid ""
"All registered SDD payments can be processed at once by uploading an XML "
"file containing a batch of all posted SDD payments to your online banking "
"interface. To do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"ניתן לעבד את כל תשלומי SDD הרשומים בבת אחת על ידי העלאת קובץ XML המכיל אצווה "
"של כל תשלומי SDD שפורסמו לממשק הבנקאות המקוון שלך. כדי לעשות זאת, בצע את "
"השלבים הבאים:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:123
msgid ""
":ref:`Create a batch payment <accounting/batch/creation>` and include the "
"SDD payments to collect."
msgstr ""
":ref:`צור תשלום באצווה <accounting/batch/creation>` וכלול את תשלומי SDD "
"לגבייה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:127
msgid ""
"You can filter payments by SDD scheme using the :guilabel:`SDD CORE` "
"and :guilabel:`SDD B2B` filters."
msgstr ""
"ניתן לסנן תשלומים לפי ערכת SDD באמצעות המסננים :guilabel:`SDD CORE` "
"ו-:guilabel:`SDD B2B`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:130
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Validate` the batch payment. The XML file is generated "
"automatically and available for download in the chatter."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`אימות` של תשלום האצווה. קובץ ה-XML נוצר אוטומטית וזמין להורדה "
"בצ'אט."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:132
msgid ""
"Download the XML file and upload it to your online banking interface to "
"process the payments."
msgstr ""
"יש להוריד את קובץ ה-XML ולהעלות אותו לממשק הבנקאות המקוון שלך כדי לעבד את "
"התשלומים."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:133
msgid ""
"Once the SDD batch payment has been received, :doc:`reconcile the "
"transaction <../bank/reconciliation>` with the batch payment to mark the "
"related invoices as :guilabel:`Paid`."
msgstr ""
"לאחר קבלת תשלום אצווה של SDD, :doc:`התאם את העסקה <../bank/reconciliation>` "
"עם תשלום האצווה כדי לסמן את החשבוניות הקשורות כ:guilabel:`שולם`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:138
msgid ""
"To view the payments and invoices linked to a specific SDD mandate, click "
"the :guilabel:`Collections` and :guilabel:`Invoices Paid` smart button on "
"the :ref:`Direct Debit Mandate <accounting/sepa_payments/sdd>` form."
msgstr ""
"כדי להציג את התשלומים והחשבוניות המקושרים להרשאת SDD ספציפית, לחץ על הכפתור "
"החכם :guilabel:`גבייות` ו:guilabel:`חשבוניות ששולמו` בטופס :ref:`הרשאת חיוב "
"ישיר <accounting/sepa_payments/sdd>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:143
msgid ""
"The files generated by Odoo comply with the SDD **PAIN.008.001.02** "
"specifications, as required by the SEPA customer-to-bank `implementation "
"guidelines <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/"
"implementation-guidelines/sepa-credit-transfer-customer-psp-"
"implementation>`_, which ensures compatibility with banks."
msgstr ""
"הקבצים שנוצרים על ידי Odoo תואמים למפרט SDD **PAIN.008.001.02**, כנדרש על "
"ידי `הנחיות היישום <https://www.europeanpaymentscouncil.eu/document-library/"
"implementation-guidelines/sepa-credit-transfer-customer-psp-"
"implementation>`_ של SEPA מלקוח לבנק, מה שמבטיח תאימות לבנקים."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:149
msgid ""
":doc:`SEPA Direct Debit for online payments <../../payment_providers/sdd>`"
msgstr ":doc:`הוראת קבע SEPA לתשלומים מקוונים <../../payment_providers/sdd>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:152
msgid "SDD rejections"
msgstr "דחיות SDD"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:154
msgid ""
"SDD rejections can occur for several reasons, the most common being "
"insufficient funds in the customer's account. With SDD, the recipient's "
"account is credited before the funds are actually debited from the "
"customer's account. As a result, if an SDD payment is later rejected, the "
"bank automatically withdraws the amount of that payment from the recipient's "
"account, and a new transaction for a negative amount is created to reflect "
"the SDD rejection."
msgstr ""
"דחיות SDD יכולות להתרחש מכמה סיבות, כאשר הנפוצה ביותר היא מחסור בכספים "
"בחשבון הלקוח. עם SDD, חשבון המקבל מזוכה לפני שהכספים למעשה מחויבים מחשבון "
"הלקוח. כתוצאה מכך, אם תשלום SDD נדחה מאוחר יותר, הבנק מושך אוטומטית את סכום "
"התשלום מחשבון המקבל, ונוצרת עסקה חדשה לסכום שלילי כדי לשקף את דחיית SDD."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:160
msgid ""
"In this case, you must reverse the journal entry associated with the "
"rejected payment and reconcile the reversal of the journal entry with the "
"transaction for the SDD rejection. To do so, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"במקרה זה, עליך לבטל את רישום היומן המשויך לתשלום שנדחה ולהתאים את ביטול "
"רישום היומן לעסקה של דחיית SDD. לשם כך, בצע את השלבים הבאים:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:164
msgid "Access the invoice linked to the rejected SDD payment."
msgstr "גש לחשבונית המקושרת לתשלום SDD שנדחה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:165
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(information)` icon in the "
"footer of the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab, then click :guilabel:`View` to "
"access the payment associated with the invoice."
msgstr ""
"לחצו על הסמל :icon:`fa-info-circle` :guilabel:`(מידע)` בתחתית "
"הלשונית :guilabel:`שורות חשבונית`, ולאחר מכן לחצו על :guilabel:`תצוגה` כדי "
"לגשת לתשלום המשויך לחשבונית."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:168
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Journal entry` smart button to access the related "
"journal entry."
msgstr ""
"לחצו על הכפתור החכם :guilabel:`רישום יומן` כדי לגשת לרישום היומן הקשור."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:169
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Reverse entry`, optionally edit the fields in the popup, "
"then click :guilabel:`Reverse`. A reversal entry is created with "
"a :guilabel:`Reference` mentioning the initial journal entry. As a result, "
"the invoice is marked as :guilabel:`Not paid`."
msgstr ""
"לחצו על :guilabel:`רישום הפוך`, ערכו באופן אופציונלי את השדות בחלון הקופץ, "
"ולאחר מכן לחצו על :guilabel:`הפוך`. רישום הפוך נוצר עם :guilabel:`הפניה` "
"המזכירה את רישום היומן הראשוני. כתוצאה מכך, החשבונית מסומנת כ:guilabel:`לא "
"שולם`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:172
msgid ""
":ref:`Access the bank journal's reconciliation view <accounting/"
"reconciliation/access>` and :ref:`reconcile <accounting/reconciliation/"
"reconcile>` the transaction created for the SDD rejection with the reversal "
"of the entry related to the payment."
msgstr ""
":ref:`גש לתצוגת ההתאמה של יומן הבנק <accounting/reconciliation/access>` "
"ו:ref:`התאם <accounting/reconciliation/reconcile>` את העסקה שנוצרה עבור "
"דחיית SDD עם ביטול הרישום הקשור לתשלום."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:179
msgid "SEPA Credit Transfer"
msgstr "העברת אשראי SEPA"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:186
msgid ""
"To pay suppliers with SCT, from the **Accounting** app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings. Under :guilabel:`Vendor "
"Payments`, activate :guilabel:`SEPA Credit Transfer (SCT)`. Next, fill out "
"your company data:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:190
msgid ":guilabel:`Your Company`: The name of the company to use SCT."
msgstr ":guilabel:`החברה שלך`: שם החברה לשימוש ב-SCT."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:191
msgid ":guilabel:`Name Identification`: The tax ID of the related company."
msgstr ":guilabel:`זיהוי שם`: מספר המס של החברה הקשורה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:192
msgid ":guilabel:`Issuer`: The name of the entity that issued the tax ID."
msgstr ":guilabel:`מנפיק`: שם הגוף שהנפיק את מספר מזהה המס."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:194
msgid ""
"After activating SEPA, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Journals` and "
"open your :guilabel:`Bank` journal. Under :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments`, "
"add :guilabel:`SEPA Credit Transfer` as a :guilabel:`Payment Method` if it's "
"not there. This allows Odoo to use this bank account to generate XML payment "
"files."
msgstr ""
"לאחר הפעלת SEPA, עבור אל :menuselection:`תצורה --> יומנים` ופתח את "
"יומן :guilabel:`הבנק` שלך. תחת :guilabel:`תשלומים יוצאים`, "
"הוסף :guilabel:`העברת אשראי SEPA` כ:guilabel:`אמצעי תשלום` אם אינו מופיע שם. "
"פעולה זו מאפשרת ל-Odoo להשתמש בחשבון בנק זה כדי ליצור קבצי תשלום XML."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:200
msgid "Registering payments"
msgstr "רישום תשלומים"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:202
msgid ""
"To register vendor payments made with SCT, first verify that "
"an :guilabel:`Account Number` and :guilabel:`Bank` are indicated on the "
"vendor's :doc:`contact form <../../../essentials/contacts>`, under "
"the :guilabel:`Accounting` tab. Odoo automatically verifies if the IBAN "
"format is respected."
msgstr ""
"כדי לרשום תשלומים לספקים שבוצעו באמצעות SCT, קודם כל ודא ש:guilabel:`מספר "
"חשבון` ו:guilabel:`בנק` מצוינים ב:doc:`טופס איש הקשר <../../../essentials/"
"contacts>` של הספק, תחת הכרטיסייה :guilabel:`חשבונאות`. Odoo מאמת אוטומטית "
"אם פורמט IBAN נשמר."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:206
msgid ""
"Then, go to :menuselection:`Vendors --> Payments`, and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. When creating your payment, select :guilabel:`SEPA "
"Credit Transfer` as the :guilabel:`Payment Method`. The :guilabel:`Vendor "
"Bank Account` is automatically populated based on the :guilabel:`Vendor` "
"selected. For future payments to this vendor, Odoo will automatically "
"suggest the bank account, but it remains possible to select a new one from "
"the dropdown menu by clicking the :guilabel:`Vendor Bank Account` field."
msgstr ""
"לאחר מכן, עבור אל :menuselection:`ספקים --> תשלומים`, ולחץ "
"על :guilabel:`חדש`. בעת יצירת התשלום שלך, בחר :guilabel:`העברת אשראי SEPA` "
"כ:guilabel:`אמצעי תשלום`. ה:guilabel:`חשבון בנק הספק` מאוכלס אוטומטית על "
"בסיס ה:guilabel:`ספק` שנבחר. עבור תשלומים עתידיים לספק זה, Odoo יציע "
"אוטומטית את חשבון הבנק, אך עדיין אפשר לבחור חשבון חדש מהתפריט הנפתח על ידי "
"לחיצה על השדה :guilabel:`חשבון בנק הספק`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:213
msgid ""
"Once your payment is registered, do not forget to confirm it. You can also "
"pay vendor bills from the bill directly using the :guilabel:`Register "
"Payment` button at the top of a vendor bill. The form is the same, but the "
"payment is directly linked to the bill and will be automatically reconciled "
"with it."
msgstr ""
"לאחר רישום התשלום שלך, אל תשכח לאשר אותו. באפשרותך גם לשלם חשבוניות ספק "
"מהחשבונית ישירות באמצעות הלחצן :guilabel:`רשום תשלום` בראש חשבונית הספק. "
"הטופס זהה, אך התשלום מקושר ישירות לחשבונית ויתואם אוטומטית איתה."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:221
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:148
msgid "ISO 20022"
msgstr "ISO 20022"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:223
msgid ""
"ISO 20022 is a global standard for the exchange of payment data between "
"banks. It uses a format that lets payment details and related documents move "
"together as a single package. This means information such as invoice "
"numbers, tax details, and who sent the payment is stored in fields that "
"computers can automatically read. Unlike SEPA, the ISO 20022 standard can be "
"used with any currency worldwide."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:228
msgid ""
"In Odoo, the SEPA Payments module acts as the underlying engine for all ISO "
"20022 transactions (both domestic SEPA payments in euros and non-euro global "
"transfers are supported by the module)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:231
msgid ""
":doc:`Some countries and regions <sepa_payments>` may use a localized, "
"country-specific version of ISO 20022, which requires additional "
"configuration. In these cases, we strongly recommend reading the :ref:`PAIN "
"version <accounting/sepa_payments/pain>` section of this page."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:238
msgid "PAIN version"
msgstr "גרסת PAIN"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:241
msgid ""
":abbr:`PAIN (PAyment INitiation)` is the specific message protocol within "
"ISO 20022 used to send transfer instructions from Odoo to your bank."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:243
msgid ""
"To enable a country-specific PAIN version, first check that you have "
"the :doc:`fiscal localization <../../../finance/fiscal_localizations>` for "
"your country installed in your database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:248
msgid ""
"ISO 20022 **PAIN.001.001.03** is being deprecated in November 2026. Make "
"sure to use the newer **PAIN.001.001.09** version or the one required in "
"your country."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:251
msgid ""
"To select a specific PAIN version, open the **Accounting** app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Journals`, and open "
"your :guilabel:`Bank` journal. Click the :guilabel:`Outgoing Payments` tab, "
"and select the :guilabel:`SEPA Pain Version` that suits your needs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:255
msgid "Reminder"
msgstr "תזכורת"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:257
msgid ""
"The SEPA payments module covers both SEPA payments *and* ISO 20022 payments."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:262
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:160
msgid "Export XML files"
msgstr "ייצוא קבצי XML"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:264
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/switzerland.rst:162
msgid ""
"To generate a daily XML payment file for upload to the online banking "
"interface, :ref:`create a batch payment <accounting/batch/creation>`. The "
"XML file is then displayed in the chatter, where it can be downloaded and "
"submitted to the bank for processing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/payments/sepa_payments.rst:268
