msgid ""
"To expand the lines of a report and view its details, click the :icon:`fa-"
"caret-right` (:guilabel:`right arrow`) on the left. Then click the :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` (:guilabel:`down arrow`) to the right of the account, journal "
"entry, payment, invoice, etc. to :guilabel:`Annotate` and view the details."
