"A list of all expense reports with a status of either :guilabel:`To "
"Submit`, :guilabel:`Submitted`, :guilabel:`Approved`, :guilabel:`Posted`, "
"or :guilabel:`Done` appears. Expense reports with a status "
"of :guilabel:`Refused` are hidden, by default."
msgstr ""
