msgstr "אישור דוחות הוצאות"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/expenses/approve_expenses.rst:31
msgid ""
"Expense reports can be approved in two ways: :ref:`individually <expenses/"
"individual>` or :ref:`in bulk <expenses/multiple>`."
msgstr ""
"ניתן לאשר דוחות הוצאות בשתי דרכים: :ref:`בנפרד <expenses/individual>` "
