#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:None
msgid "TPAR fiscal position"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/australia.rst:341
msgid ""
"Upon billing a contact with a fiscal position set to :guilabel:`TPAR` "
"or :guilabel:`TPAR without ABN`, the report is automatically generated "
"in :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> Taxable Payments Annual "
