msgid "The total amount of VAT included is **less** than **400 EUR**."
msgstr "הסכום הכולל של מע\"מ כלול הוא **פחות** מ-**400 יורו**."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/italy.rst:411
msgid ""
"The 400 EUR threshold was defined in `the decree of the 10th of May 2019 in "
"the Gazzetta Ufficiale <https://www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/"
"2019/05/24/19A03271/sg>`_. We advise you to check the current official value."
msgstr ""
"סף 400 היורו הוגדר ב`צו מה-10 במאי 2019 ב-Gazzetta Ufficiale <https://"
"www.gazzettaufficiale.it/eli/id/2019/05/24/19A03271/sg>`_. אנו ממליצים לך "
"לבדוק את הערך הרשמי הנוכחי."

