"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Accounting --> Electronic Invoicing (MX)`. "
"Under the :guilabel:`MX PAC` section, enter the name of your |PAC| with your "
"credentials (:guilabel:`PAC username` and :guilabel:`PAC password`)."
