#~ "account is credited before the funds are actually debited from the "
#~ "customer's account. As a result, if an |sdd| payment is later rejected, "
#~ "the bank automatically withdraws the amount of that payment from the "
#~ "recipient's account, and a new transaction for a negative amount is "
#~ "created to reflect the |sdd| rejection."
